rns under the RSWM EDGE brand name. It also exports synthetic, blended, melange, cotton, and specialty value-added yarns. The company was formerly known as Rajasthan Spinning & Weaving Mills Ltd. RSWM Limited was incorporated in 1960 and is headquartered in Noida, India."}}